author: Rosie
name: EventLogger
install_msg:
Thank you for installing the EventLogger cog!
Do `[p]help EventLogger` to get the list of commands and their description. If you want to help translate, go to my [crowdin](<https://crowdin.com/project/Star-Cogs>)
If you like my work, [donate me!](<https://ko-fi.com/starcogs>)

This cog allows you to log various Discord events in specified channels.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any user data persistently. It only logs Discord events as they occur.
